	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64600533">While we're at it, I want my leaded gasoline back.  The lead lubricated multiple assemblies in the head of big-block engines, I don't care if lead tetraethyl is toxic and gets in everyone's air, even in Antarctica.<p>
And I don't care of somebody's male children start growing boobs because of a perfectly profit-improving additive that also happens to have binding sites not too different from estrogen.  Only, wait . . . isn't this <i>explicitly</i> what we want our government to do?  Isn't this <i>exactly</i> what we want ou<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
